{"tid":2160502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"佐敦藍店 鐵板燒  有證據扮黃呃生意","createTime":"2020-08-17T04:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T08:30:15.000Z","uid":33586,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"90e364d60310f9a3fa5e92a6a4617c2fa6610c85","tid":2160502,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:00:33.000Z","msg":"係終極黃藍地圖copy過嚟 等多啲人睇到<br />\n落返credit: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/101032584814848/posts/175107694074003/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F101032584814848%2Fposts%2F175107694074003%2F&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=6e7bfea0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/101032584814848/posts/175107694074003/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>《黃店轉藍通知－S2鐵板燒》</strong></span><br />\n自從7月起我地將黃店原因隱藏，目的係為咗保護黃店，但咁做同樣降低咗我地做事嘅透明度，尤其是黃藍店轉色原因。有見及此，我地決定以後將商戶由黃轉藍嘅決定，按情況獨立出post解釋。[註1]<br />\n<br />\n店舖名稱：S2鐵板燒<br />\n位處地區：佐敦<br />\n<br />\n【原有黃店原因】<br />\n1. 5/8 老闆樂師傅出post表示所有員工放假一天，不當曠工，開放俾人飲水休息並hashtag #香港人加油<br />\n2. 5/10, 6/10 休市<br />\n3. 推出為香港人打氣活動<br />\n<br />\n【轉為藍店原因】<br />\n之前因為有網友報料指店舖在某些日子為了支持示威而休息，故當時將店舖列作黃店。後來有網友報料店舖指5/8並非休息，而是有開鋪繼續營業。至於5/10及6/10兩日店舖休息，經過我們重新查證後，發現店舖無說明休息原因，未能確定立場；反而我們收到多項證據顯示老闆會指責示威者。因此我們最後將店舖列入藍店。<br />\n<br />\n【現時藍店原因】（請參考下列對應的証據）<br />\n1. 5/8並非真休息，老闆自己承認係藉口&amp;會坐鎮餐廳正常營業。另外員工表示假期是自己請的，並非額外假期。<br />\n2. 所謂嘅文宣只係老闆唔比我地痴喺公司門口，跟住我地要鬼鼠地黐喺隔離吉舖<br />\n3. 表明不希望在蘋果動出現，只因希望打入大陸市場<br />\n4. 12/8 和你飛行動後於whatsapp責罵員工放假入機場<br />\n5. 親中商會過黎食飯，佢會要求所有員工要在身上貼上國旗，佢自己亦有貼國旗係身<br />\n<br />\n1. <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QZDvWoI7vpxpeCdSJ9oNKmBrxMq80NUU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1QZDvWoI7vpxpeCdSJ9oNKmBrxMq80NUU%2F&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=aecf9bfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QZDvWoI7vpxpeCdSJ9oNKmBrxMq80NUU/</a><br />\n2. <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1RQnZXKjj8YW3anTw-RK7XSfeUR8QJC1R/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1RQnZXKjj8YW3anTw-RK7XSfeUR8QJC1R%2F&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=1ae18aa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1RQnZXKjj8YW3anTw-RK7XSfeUR8QJC1R/</a><br />\n3. <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1sueR0_f-leyvYcODT9MKF3NxcflTHv-D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1sueR0_f-leyvYcODT9MKF3NxcflTHv-D%2F&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=45edc5e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1sueR0_f-leyvYcODT9MKF3NxcflTHv-D/</a><br />\n4. <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1k87WllNtVuIHEouwxdv8FJ2QHhPshwQn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1k87WllNtVuIHEouwxdv8FJ2QHhPshwQn%2F&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=d8bea304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1k87WllNtVuIHEouwxdv8FJ2QHhPshwQn/</a><br />\n5. <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1nelMcwucSuz4UhJexxDgYZtIBibppZE_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1nelMcwucSuz4UhJexxDgYZtIBibppZE_%2F&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=2c4b88eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1nelMcwucSuz4UhJexxDgYZtIBibppZE_/</a><br />\n<br />\n終極黃藍地圖一直以發布最準確的黃藍店資訊為最大原則，但由於資訊量龐大，Fact-check工作或有錯漏之處。感謝各位網友、同路人嘅提點，令到資訊更加完整！<br />\n本Post下的留言，管理員不會一一回覆，如果你就S2鐵板燒轉色一事，有更多資訊提供，請填寫報料Google form！我地會繼續跟進～<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n報料form: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/U5B1gJnEY4sBqJNg9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FU5B1gJnEY4sBqJNg9&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=28b28c35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/U5B1gJnEY4sBqJNg9</a><br />\n最好留返個contact，等我地有嘢可以問返你<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n[註1]：如果有黃店被揭發黃店証據不足／偽黃，而網上其他黃店平台已有豐富的討論內容，終極黃藍地圖將不會獨立出post解釋，以免資訊泛濫。<br />\n<br />\n［註2］：中環店S2 kitchen與佐敦店為不同經營者。"},{"pid":"444a9d18f89c2b5278be50a86361f3eddae27800","tid":2160502,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:02:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"689999520bf99260cf7905141fe80428233566b0","tid":2160502,"uid":33586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:02:59.000Z","msg":"費時比佢呃 仲要長期播cctvb"},{"pid":"59f58a42cfce76f9ba303feacf70892c4244ed0b","tid":2160502,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:13:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c864c8fc23dcc61d781cb73ad3b25bb8b43d8d91","tid":2160502,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4388198d0b2aa790eab510af2e699c78f8aef35d","tid":2160502,"uid":304431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4590243c7787b0e660868b1cef9ccbf285386325","tid":2160502,"uid":67655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a2abc298091296b8342c04c1755d9d5774281f","tid":2160502,"uid":1191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:14:55.00